translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  47,20,Jo log iman laye hain woh keh rahe thay ke koi surat kyun nahin nazil ki jaati (jis mein jung ka hukum diya jaye) magar jab ek mohkam surat nazil kardi gayi jismein jung ka zikr tha to tumne dekha ke jinke dilon mein bimari thi woh tumhari taraf is tarah dekh rahey hain jaise kisi par maut chaa gayi ho. Afsos unke haal par
  47,21,(Unki zubaan par hai) itaat ka ikrar aur acchi acchi batein. Magar jab qataii hukum de diya gaya us waqt woh Allah se apne ahad mein sacche nikalte to unhi ke liye accha tha
  47,22,Ab kya tum logon se iske siwa kuch aur tawaqqu ki ja sakti hai ke agar tum ulte mooh phir gaye to zameen mein phir fasad barpa karoge aur aapas mein ek dusre ke galay (throats) kaatoge
  47,23,Yeh log hain jinpar Allah ne laanat ki aur inko andha (blind) aur behra bana diya
  47,24,"Kya un logon ne Quran par gaur nahin kiya, ya dilon par unke qufal (locks) chade huey hain"
  47,25,Haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log hidayat wazeh ho jaane ke baad ussey phir gaye unke liye shaytan ne is rawish ko sahal bana diya hai aur jhuti tawaqquat ka silsila unke liye daraaz kar rakkha hai
  47,26,Is liye unhon ne Allah ke nazil karda deen ko napasand karne walon se kehdiya ke baaz maamlaat mein hum tumhari manenge.Allah unki yeh khufiya baatein khoob jaanta hai
  47,27,Phir us waqt kya haal hoga jab farishtey inki roohein qabz karenge aur inke mooh aur peethon (backs) par maarte huey inhein le jayenge
  47,28,Yeh isi liye to hoga ke inhon ne us tariqe ki pairwi ki jo Allah ko naraaz karne wala hai aur us ki raza ka raasta ikhtiyar karna pasand na kiya. Isi bina par usne inke sab aamaal zaya kar diye
  47,29,Kya woh log jinke dilon mein bimari hai yeh samjhe baithe hain ke Allah unke dilon ke khot (keena) zahir nahin karega